{"tid":1605233,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"用Galaxy Fold玩瑪奇Mobile...遊戲製作人：Galaxy Fold都唔好用嘅","createTime":"2019-09-30T08:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T13:12:44.000Z","uid":109923,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ad737185b30a6d3b9a2314cf899e4c6ce18983d8","tid":1605233,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:21:33.000Z","msg":"갤럭시폴드로 마비노기모바일하면 좋다. (그 외엔 별루다)<br />\nGalaxy Fold用嚟玩瑪奇Mobile幾好呀(除此之外都麻麻地)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wJj8Uj7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwJj8Uj7.jpg&h=147a68b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n갤럭시폴드Galaxy Fold의 단점短點 랭킹ranking(물론 알고 샀다)<br />\nGalaxy Fold缺點排名(梗係我買嫁啦)<br />\n<br />\n1. 방수防水 안됨不能 = 唔防水<br />\n2. 무겁重고 접折으면 두꺼움厚 = 重 &amp; 折埋變到好厚<br />\n3. 키보드keyboard 입력入力 애매曖昧함 = 鍵盤輸入模糊<br />\n4. 덱스DeX 안됨不能 = 用唔到Samsung DeX <br />\n5. 비율比率 안맞不對는 앱들App이 고통苦痛스럽게 함 = 比例唔嘅啱App用得好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n장점長點 = 優點<br />\n1. 내 게임이 폼나게 돈다 我隻GAME華麗轉身"},{"pid":"1c8f84ffd7b24a41457f5e70fe474d3d04c8e4c3","tid":1605233,"uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:25:05.000Z","msg":"三叔出咗啦，華為幾時抄好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「敵不動 我不動」華為摺機 Mate X 需再次延期發售 　起碼要等到11月之後<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1486418</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a96833e02881ce4e29c4c79294dbe8290ebc1850","tid":1605233,"uid":53036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:40:40.000Z","msg":"呢隻驚講左有無3年？<br />\n<br />\n完全無影"},{"pid":"daff8d1b63cb5c07cbf4e943811e5b1f372f8f5c","tid":1605233,"uid":119478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a96833e02881ce4e29c4c79294dbe8290ebc1850","tid":1605233,"uid":53036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:40:40.000Z","msg":"呢隻驚講左有無3年？<br />\n<br />\n完全無影"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:42:28.000Z","msg":"韓國